Aim_ogc_map

As per request, I have made the official map for an online aim competition in New Zealand, called "aim_ogc_map", for "OGC NZ" Online Gaming Competition (www.ogc.net.nz).

-	6 Spawn points, 3 per team
-	Both the Colt and Ak47 weapons are stacked on the ground under each spawn point.
-	Each player also starts with a Deagle pistol, knife, and kevlar vest.
-	No Buy Zones
-	Contains an overview radar
-	3d Skybox
-	Nav File for bots
-	Optimized with No Draw for better FPS
-	All files compiled into the .bsp using Pakrat

Blair (Bobpoblo) Burkhardt - Level Design
http://www.fpsbanana.com/members/776402
